deck: Luthor and the Flash switch bodies. Doctor Light, Steel, and Ice leave on a mission to put it right, while the rest of the League must deal with Lex Luthor at super-speed.
name: The Great Brain Robbery

deck: A small group of Japanese, allied with some members of the Chinese Federation, attack Kyushu. Lelouch, however, does not feel that their interests are the same as his.
name: Battle at Kyushu

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description: Thor is attacked by a powerful creature known as Beta Ray Bill - who proves himself just as able to lift and wield Mjölnir. Thor and Sif soon finds themselves allying with this strange warrior (who apparently has his own reasons for disliking Surtur) to save all of Asgard from being burned to the ground by the demon lord of Muspelheim.
name: The Ballad of Beta Ray Bill

deck: Buttercup addresses her anger issues.
description:
Plot Summary

After being accused of being too violent and quick to anger, Buttercup resolves to improve herself.
name: Makes Zen to Me

description: Nick Fury returns, having assembled a team of heroes in secret (him, Black Widow, Mockingbird, and Quake) to gather information about the impending Skrull invasion of Earth.
name: Who Do You Trust?

deck: Roulette reinstates Metabrawl matches and focuses on all female fights, using brainwashed Justice League members as the combatants.
description:
Roulette brings Metabrawl back with a totally female fight card.

Huntress vs. Black Canary

Vixen vs. Hawkgirl

Huntress, Black Canary, Vixen, and Hawkgirl vs. Wonder Woman
name: Grudge Match

deck: The Ashford Academy holds their annual festival. Suzaku and Kallen agree not to be enemies at school. Euphemia sneaks onto the campus to talk to her half-siblings, Lelouch and Nunnally, about the past - and the future.
name: The School Festival Declaration

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description: After being a prisoner of the Skrulls for months, Captain America teams up with other prisoners, including some of his enemies, to escape. But in order to do so, they must first get past the mighty Super-Skrull...
name: Prisoner of War

deck: Euphemia, with Suzaku at her side, opens the Special Administrated Zone of Japan, where Elevens are allowed to express their Japanese culture. Euphemia asks for Zero's support, in the hope that she and Lelouch can be allies. Lelouch has to think of how do deal with the situation.
name: Bloodstaine Euphy

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

deck: Green Lantern, Supergirl, and Green Arrow are kidnapped by Brainiac 5 of the Legion of Super-Heroes.
name: Far From Home

description: A mysterious red-skinned Hulk attacks the S.H.I.E.L.D. Helicarrier. While Wasp and Captain America fight this new behemoth (who Maria Hill fervently believes is the Hulk gone rogue), Hawkeye attempts to keep a resistant Bruce Banner safe.
name: Nightmare in Red

deck: Lelouch, regrettably, has to take responsibility for what he accidentally did to Euphemia.
name: At Least with Sorrow

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description: The Skrulls' invasion of Earth has begun - and Wakanda is the first target. Ms. Marvel comes to the rescue, but must deal with both a stubborn Black Panther and a team of Skrulls posing as the Avengers.
name: Infiltration

deck: Shadow Thief captures Green Lantern, Hawkgirl, and Hawkman. We learn more about Hawkgirl's past in ancient Egypt.
name: Ancient History

deck: Lelouch deals major damage to Cornelia's forces during his invasion of Tokyo. Suzaku seeks revenge on Zero.
name: The Collapsing Stage

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

deck: Lelouch finally confronts Cornelia face-to-face, and uses his Geass to finally learn the truth about his mother's murder.
name: Zero

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

deck: In an attempt to reassemble Brainiac, Lex Luthor accidentally resurrects Darkseid.
name: Alive!

deck: It has been a year since the Battle of Tokyo. Lelouch is just a normal student, living with his little brother at Ashford Academy. But if he's so normal, why is he being hunted?
name: The Day a Demon Awakens

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

deck: The Justice League and Secret Society form a temporary alliance in order to halt Darkseid's forces as they invade Earth. Martian Manhunter returns to join the fight.
name: Destroyer

deck: With his memories restored, Lelouch becomes Zero once more, and leads his small remnant of Black Knights out of certain death.
name: Plan for Independent Japan

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description: The Skrulls have invaded the entire planet and are using Captain America's position of respect to convince the humans to submit. When Hawkeye, Wasp, and Ms. Marvel are captured by Veranke's army of Super-Skrulls, all seems lost - until Iron Man and Thor are reunited with the real Captain America in a last-ditch effort to drive back the Skrull onslaught and save Earth.
name: Secret Invasion

deck: Lelouch comes under suspicion when those watching him think his memories have returned. Lelouch has to figure out how to get around them... and figure out who Rolo, his "little brother," really is.
name: Imprisoned in Campus

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description: Captain America teams up with the equally mistrusted Spider-Man to fight the Serpent Society when they try to rescue Viper and King Cobra from S.H.I.E.L.D. custody.
name: Along Came A Spider...

deck: Lelouch stages a plan to rescue the leaders of the Black Knights from the execution grounds, intent on restoring his group. But first, he has to escape Rolo...
name: Counterattack at the Gallows

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description: With Thor and Hawkeye in tow, Captain America travels to Wakanda to have his shield repaired and to persuade Black Panther to rejoin the team. But a mysterious figure known only as the Vision arrives to steal the shield - along with Wakanda's supply of vibranium.
name: Behold, The Vision

deck: Suzaku returns to Ashford Academy to make sure Lelouch's memories have not returned. He brings with him two other members of the Knights of the Round.
name: Knights of the Round

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

deck: Lelouch is cornered: reveal his identity to Suzaku, or lie to Nunnally.
name: Surprise Attack over the Pacific

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

deck: Lelouch becomes distraught when he sees that Nunnally fears Zero, and instead goes to Suzaku's side. He considers giving up his identity as Zero.
name: The Abandoned Mask

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

deck: Zero accepts Viceroy Nunnally's offer to take part in the new Special Administrated Zone. However, he has something else up his sleeve.
name: One Million Miracles

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

deck: The Black Knights take up residence in the Chinese Federation. However, Prince Schneizel sets up a plan that could destroy everything.
name: A Bride in the Vermillion Forbidden City

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

deck: Lelouch is able to stop the wedding between the Chinese Empress and the Britannian Prince Odysseus. But his plan is interfered when Xingke, the Empress' primary guard, tries to rescue her in a powerful prototype Knightmare.
name: When Shen Hu Wins Glory

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

deck: The Black Knights are cornered by Chinese forces, while Britannia is forbidden to intervene. Lelouch must hatch a plan to escape his situation. Meanwhile, Kallen is taken prisoner by Britannia.
name: Power of Passion

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

deck: Buffy moves to Sunnydale and meets Willow, Giles and Xander
description: Buffy moves to Sunnydale and meets Willow, Giles and Xander.
name: Welcome to the Hellmouth

deck: Buffy has to fight Luke to stop The Master from rising.
description: Buffy fights the minions of a centuries-old vampire called 'The Master'.
name: The Harvest

deck: Buffy becomes a cheerleader and a witch casts a spell on her.
description: Buffy and her friends have to fight a witch who's determined to be a cheerleader.
name: Witch

deck: Buffy must save Xander from a giant praying mantis
description: Buffy fights a giant praying mantis.
name: Teacher's Pet

description: The young heroes offically becomes a team and must learn to work together and combat Mister Twister.
name: Welcome to Happy Harbor

deck: Lelouch returns to Ashford Academy, only to find out that his body-double has been acting far more affectionate than Lelouch would, leading to unwanted affection from some of the girls on campus. Milly is graduating Ashford Academy.
name: Love Attack!

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description: The team goes on their first covert mission, but who is leading the team?
name: Drop Zone

description: Superboy is still in his angry phase which makes teamwork hard when they must battle Dr. Ivo's Amazo robot.
name: Schooled

description: New teammate Artemis must prover herself to everyone on the team especially fellow archer Red Arrow.
name: Infiltrator

description: Wally must come to terms with his scientific view of the world and the mystical side when the team must find Kent Nelson aka Dr. Fate.
name: Denial

description: Batman tells Aqualad to choose to live life under the sea or on the surface world, as this doubt was hindering his ability to perform as a good leader. Aqualad goes to Atlantis to meet up with his old pals Garth and Tula. However, this is cut short when Black Manta invades the Atlantean Science Center to obtain the giant starfish creature. Meanwhile, the other members of the Team are enjoying the downtime with friends and family.
name: Downtime

description: The team wakes up in Bialya with no memory from the past 6 months. They must recover their memories and relearn how to work together.
name: Bereft

description: Roy Harper works on his own to try and stop the League of Assassins from stoping the peace treaty between two nations.
name: Targets

deck: Jeremiah Gottwald returns in a new cyborg body, hunting Lelouch on the Ashford campus and threatening the students. Shirley regains her memories that Lelouch is Zero.
name: Assassin from the Past

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description: The Enchantress offers Loki a chance to exact his revenge on Thor and the Avengers for thwarting his conquest of the Nine Realms, and uses a spell to strip Thor, Captain America, and Iron Man of their powers. Now, the helpless heroes must defeat Loki - his soul now in command of a powerful Asgardian weapon known as the Destroyer - without their abilities.
name: Powerless

deck: Lelouch seeks vengeance against all of Geass itself because of Shirley's death. To that end, with the aid of Jeremiah - who joined Lelouch - Lelouch attacks the headquarters of the Geass Order, intent on capturing V.V.
name: Geass Hunt

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description: Stranded in the Negative Zone, the Avengers must join forces with their enemies - including former members of the Masters of Evil - to fight off an army of strange insectoid creatures that are laying siege to 42.
name: Assault on 42

description: Superboy and Miss Martian go undercover in Belle Reve prison to find out who is organizing super villians.
name: Terrors

deck: At the Hulk's Cave Rick Jones develops floating cameras to film the Hulk's heroic feats in the style of a reality TV show. Annihilus arrives in Vista Verde to gather the siphon the gamma energy in order to invade Earth however what Annihilus has planned and what grave force he has at his finger tips will definitely challenge The Hulk.
name: Doorway to Destruction Part 1

series.name: Hulk and the Agents of S.M.A.S.H.

deck: Lelouch is transported to another plane of existence, where he confronts his father.
name: The C's World

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description: The Cave is attacked by two robots taking everyone but Robin and Artemis out of action. Now the powerless team members have to combat killer robots.
name: Homefront

description: The team is still rattled after the attack on the Cave and the revelation that Aquald with held information. Now the team must travel to India to discover why animals are running rampant.
name: Alpha Male

description: The Injustice Society reveals themselves and threatens the world. With the League occupied, it's up to the team to take down this alliance of Super Villains.
name: Revelation

description: The team believes that Red Tornado is the spy and kidnap Zatanna to help them track their robotic mentor.
name: Humanity

description: The Justice League is decimated by a mysterious alien threat, forcing the Team to step out of the shadows and become the saviors of earth.
name: Failsafe

description: Superboy's pet, Sphere, begins to act even odder than it already does. The sphere's original owners, inhabitants of New Genesis, come to Earth and want it back, as do their rivals from Apokolips.
name: Disordered

description: Zatanna and Artemis head out for a girls night out on Halloween and get dragged into supernatural events.
name: Secrets

deck: C.C. loses the majority of her memories, becoming the slave she once was. Lelouch and his allies establish the United Federation of Nations to defy Britannia. Meanwhile, the majority of the Knights of the Round - including the Knight of One - come to Japan.
name: United Federation of Nations Resolution Number One

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description: The Avengers are ambushed and captured, one by one, by Ultron's team of synthezoid Avengers as part of the wayward android's plan to rid the world of "flawed" humans, perfect himself, and construct a mate.
name: Ultron Unlimited

description: All the adults on earth suddenly vanish leaving the Team to take care of a world without adults.
name: Misplaced

description: While the team is off combating an alliance of ice based villians Kid Flash is tasked with running cross country to deliver a life saving heart.
name: Coldhearted

description: While traveling to Qurac the Team comes across a wild life presever that is important too Miss Martian. Miss Martian must come to terms with how she truly appears versus the one she chooses.
name: Image

deck: Lelouch meets with Suzaku, confirming that he regained his memories, in the hopes that Suzaku will help him in his time of need - not for Lelouch's sake, but for Nunnally's safety.
name: The Taste of Humiliation

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description: Superboy travesl back to the Cadmus facility in order to uncover more about his creationPlease use punctuation.
name: Agendas

description: Red Arrow rejoins the team which pushes Artemis into a tough spot. At the same time she must deal with fighting her older sister Cheshire.
name: Insecurity

description: The team goes undercover with the Haley Circus to determine wether the travelling circus is responsible for a rash of high tech international thefts.
name: Performance

description: All of the teams' many secretes are exposed and brought into the Light.
name: Usual Suspects

description: The mole is finally revealed as the Lights plans come to pass and have long reaching consequences.
name: Auld Acquaintance

description: A mysterious explosion seemingly kills Hank in his college laboratory, but as the Avengers and their friends mourn the loss of their fallen comrade-in-arms, a fearless new vigilante - endowed with the same powers and technology as Ant-Man/Giant-Man and Wasp and calling himself "Yellowjacket" - begins taking out the members of the Serpent Society.
name: Yellowjacket

deck: Lelouch, seemingly betrayed by Suzaku, takes steps to save Nunnally himself while the Black Knights invade Tokyo for the second time.
name: Final Battle Tokyo II

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description:
The Vision awakens after a month of repairs to find that Tony Stark and his fellow Avengers have taken over the world. With the whole planet turned against him, the Vision must get to the bottom of Tony Stark's "utopia" - only to discover an unlikely figure to be the true power behind the Avengers' throne.

Based on the 1987 Marvel graphic novel Emperor Doom (albeit with a different cast).
name: Emperor Stark

deck: Lelouch loses his will to continue when Nunnally is apparently consumed by the FLEIJA warhead. Prince Schneizel approaches the Black Knights, revealing that Zero is Lelouch.
name: Betrayal

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description:
Strange fumes sicken all of the Avengers - save for Iron Man, whose suit of armor provides him with protection.

Based on Avengers: Red Zone.
name: Code Red

deck: Emperor Charles zi Britannia enters his endgame, and Lelouch intends to stop him. When he realizes what he wants to do, Suzaku also goes after the Emperor.
name: Emperor Dismissed

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description: Captain America ponders the mystery of the Winter Soldier and enlists Nick Fury's aid to find him when the Red Skull escapes from prison and massive robots - the Sleepers - arise as part of a contingency plan by the founder of HYDRA to destroy Washington, D.C.
name: Winter Soldier

deck: Darkwing battles Quackerjack
name: Days of Blunder

deck: Lelouch, Suzaku, C.C., Lady Marianne, and Charles are together, deciding the fate of the future.
name: The Ragnarok Connection

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description: When the Hulk's name is cleared of the crimes committed by the Red Hulk, the Avengers find that the deception put forth by Captain America's Skrull doppelganger has made the green-skinned juggernaut even more of a loose cannon than before.
name: The Deadliest Man Alive

description: Clark and Pete apply to community work in an institute for the aged to be close to Lana Lang who's also volunteering there. Clark's favorite patient is Cassandra Carver, a blind old lady that foretells the future, and who realizes that Clark is not from this world. Lana takes care of Harry Bollston, an unknown former murder. When Harry falls in a lake full of kryptonite nearby the institution, he becomes young again. The young Harry Volk then seeks revenge against the descendants of the members of the jury that sentenced him in the past by killing them. One of these descendants is Jonathan Kent. Meanwhile, Lex approaches Cassandra to ask her information about Clark, and she has a vision of disaster involving Lex.
name: Hourglass

deck: With C.C. at his side and Suzaku as his Knight, Lelouch reigns as the Emperor of Britannia after his father's death.
name: Emperor Lelouch

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description: Kang the Conqueror is freed from prison by his alternate timeline doppelgangers and attempts to conquer the world once again, this time trapping the Avengers in a temporal void to keep them from getting in the way of his plans. Now a new team of heroes (Spider-Man, War Machine, Wolverine, Iron Fist, Luke Cage, and the Thing) must band together to stop the cross-temporal onslaught.
name: New Avengers

deck: Schneizel allies a group of Britannians and the Black Knights against Lelouch. The final battle begins.
name: The Schneizel's Guise

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description:
The Kree attempt to create a wormhole connecting Earth's solar system with their galaxy, which will consequently destroy the Sun and all life on Earth - just as Kang the Conqueror predicted. The Avengers and Captain Marvel head into space to stop it.

Note: The title of this episode is named after the 1992 crossover storyline of the same name.
name: Operation: Galactic Storm

deck: The battle continues. Lelouch comes up with a plan to enter the powerful battlestation of Damocles. Suzaku and Kallen begin their final duel.
name: The Grip of Damocles

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

description: The Avengers arrive on the Kree homeworld of Hala, but find that they aren't exactly welcome there - even with Captain Marvel on their side.
name: Live Kree or Die

description: The Avengers must bring forth an army of nearly all their allies to face their greatest challenge yet - Galactus, the devourer of countless worlds and civilizations, and his quartet of heralds drawn from the very elements of nature.
name: Avengers Assemble!

deck: Lelouch confronts Nunnally, who refuses to give up the Damocles Key. He is forced with a decision: lose the battle, or use his Geass on his sister?
name: Re;

series.name: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion

deck: Negaduck assembles the Fearsome Five and takes over St. Canard. Can Darkwing and the other heroes fight them?
name: Just Us Justice Ducks: Part 1

deck: Integra releases Alucard after a hundred years. Ten years later, Alucard takes an interest in a police girl, who is being attacked by vampires.
description: During a mission to eradicate a vampire priest and his minions, Arucard is forced into a difficult decision upon encountering an injured police woman. Later, Father Alexander Anderson and Arucard clash for the first time.
name: Hellsing I

deck: The Hellsing mansion comes under attack by two artificial Vampires and their army of ghouls.
description: Two daring vampire brothers lead a violent raid on the Hellsing compound. The carnage is great, but Arucard and company manage to gain a key piece of information while turning the battle’s tide.
name: Hellsing II

deck: Integra recruits a group of mercenaries to work for Hellsing in the aftermath of the Valentine attack. Integra meets with Enrico Maxwell, head of Iscariot, to find information on "Millennium." The trail leads Alucard to Brazil.
description: The Hellsing organization resorts to the recruitment of mercenaries in the wake of a devastating attack on headquarters, and Integra’s suspicions concerning the origins of their enemy are confirmed.
name: Hellsing III

deck: Negaduck assembles the Fearsome Five and takes over St. Canard. Can Darkwing and the other heroes fight them?
name: Just Us Justice Ducks: Part 2

deck: Hellsing and Iscariot meet with the Queen of England regarding the existence of Millennium. However, their meeting is interrupted when the Major, the leader of Millennium, threatens to attack England.
description: An important meeting between Hellsing and the Queen is interrupted by tidings of impending war. Meanwhile, Arucard is sent to deal with the deviants responsible for the hijacking of an aircraft carrier.
name: Hellsing IV

deck: While Alucard is stranded at sea, Millennium begins their invasion of England.
description: While Arucard is trapped aboard an aircraft carrier, London is plagued by a gruesome vampire onslaught. Elsewhere, Integra narrowly escapes a hoard of Nazi vampires.
name: Hellsing V
